# Go backend — admin

Follow [../AGENTS.md](../AGENTS.md). Transport stays thin; orchestration in `internal/admin/service/`.

## Range loops (Go 1.22+)

Do **not** copy the range variable before append/map calls:

```go
// bad — leftover pre-1.22 closure workaround
for _, item := range items {
    x := item
    out = append(out, toProto(x))
}

// good
for _, item := range items {
    out = append(out, toProto(item))
}
```

Per-iteration loop variables are already distinct; extra copies add noise only.
